True`.\n-\n-## Fix Applied\n-\n-### Phase 1: ✅ Campaign unstuck\n-Direct Firestore update cleared the stuck flags.\n-\n-### Phase 2: ✅ Code fix in _build_initial_game_state\n-Added check for `player_character_data.get(\"name\")` at world_logic.py:4919-4945:\n-```python\n-character_has_name = bool(\n-    player_character_data and isinstance(player_character_data, dict) and player_character_data.get(\"name\")\n-)\n-if character_has_name:\n-    # Character is pre-populated (god_mode/paste flow) - skip character creation modal\n-    custom_campaign_state = {\n-        \"attribute_system\": attribute_system,\n-        \"character_creation_in_progress\": False,\n-        \"character_creation_completed\": True,\n-        \"character_creation_stage\": \"complete\",\n-    }\n-else:\n-    # Character will be built from scratch (wizard flow)\n-    custom_campaign_state = {\n-        \"attribute_system\": attribute_system,\n-        \"character_creation_in_progress\": True,\n-        \"character_creation_stage\": character_creation_stage,\n-    }\n-```\n-\n-### Phase 3: ✅ Test added (commit 73bc30511)\n-Added `TestPasteCharacterCampaignSkipsModal` class with:\n-- `test_paste_character_campaign_skips_creation_modal`: verifies pre-populated character skips modal\n-- `test_character_auto_generated_still_skips_modal`: verifies auto-generated character skips modal\n-\n-## Tests\n-\n-- `test_world_logic.py`: 244 passed\n-- `test_modal_integration.py`: 10 passed\n-- `test_modal_agent_critical_bugs.py`: 8 passed\n-\n-## Status\n-\n-- [x] Root cause identified\n-- [x] Phase 1: Campaign unstuck (Firestore update)\n-- [x] Phase 2: Code fix in _build_initial_game_state\n-- [x] Phase 3: Tests added\n-- [x] Commits pushed\n-\n-## Related Issue\n-\n-- `rev-r","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false,"persistedOutputPath":"/Users/jleechan/.claude/projects/-Users-jleechan-autoresearch-main-workspace/47505249-54d8-47bd-9057-90c6dad053a3/tool-results/bhknlflq2.txt"